summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Milwaukee Land Company, an Iowa Corporation, to certain lands in Section Four (4), Township Twenty-two (22) North, Range Eight (8) East, W. M., in Cedar River Watershed, King County, Washington, and appropriating Six Hundred Twenty-seven and Thirty-nine One-hundredths ($627.39) Dollars, from Cedar River Watershed Condemnation Fund for the payment of said lands.
